homepage.quotes.christopher-chedeau.message: I've helped open source many projects at Facebook and every one needed a website. They all had very similar constraints: the documentation should be written in markdown and be deployed via GitHub pages. I‚Äôm so glad that Docusaurus now exists so that I don‚Äôt have to spend a week each time spinning up a new one.

homepage.quotes.hector-ramos.title.description: Title of quote of Hector Ramos on the home page

homepage.quotes.hector-ramos.message: Open source contributions to the React Native docs have skyrocketed after our move to Docusaurus. The docs are now hosted on a small repo in plain markdown, with none of the clutter that a typical static site generator would require. Thanks Slash!
homepage.quotes.hector-ramos.description: Quote of Hector Ramos on the home page

homepage.quotes.risky-vetter.title.description: Title of quote of Ricky Vetter on the home page

homepage.quotes.risky-vetter.message: Docusaurus has been a great choice for the ReasonML family of projects. It makes our documentation consistent, i18n-friendly, easy to maintain, and friendly for new contributors.
homepage.quotes.risky-vetter.description: Quote of Ricky Vetter on the home page

homepage.hero.title.description: Home page hero title, can contain simple html tags

Save time and focus on your project's do.message: Save time and focus on your project's documentation. Simply write docs and blog posts with Markdown/MDX and Docusaurus will publish a set of static HTML files ready to serve. You can even embed JSX components into your Markdown thanks to MDX.

Extend or customize your project's layou.message: Extend or customize your project's layout by reusing React. Docusaurus can be extended while reusing the same header and footer.

Localization comes pre-configured. Use C.message: Localization comes pre-configured. Use Crowdin to translate your docs into over 70 languages.

Support users on all versions of your pr.message: Support users on all versions of your project. Document versioning helps you keep documentation in sync with project releases.

Make it easy for your community to find.message: Make it easy for your community to find what they need in your documentation. We proudly support Algolia documentation search.
